eu_initiatives:
We are specifically interested in initiatives, policies and legislative files which pertain to the following priorities:  
- Urban and Regional Development;  
- Energy;  
- Transport;  
- Climate change adaptation;  
- Nature-based solutions;  
- Cultural Heritage-led Regeneration;  
- Smart cities;  
- Bioeconomy and circular economy;  
- Social innovation.

relevant_communication:
Our current portfolio of projects relevant to the above consists of:  
- Horizon 2020 projects (SCC1 Stardust - 
 coordinator of FC Cluj-Napoca, ProGIreg, ROCK);  
- Interreg Danube Projects (ATTRACTIVE DANUBE);  
- Several URBACT projects for which we offer assistance to cities;  
- EC Expertise for the MAC Pozzuoli Urban Innovative Actions project;
